Title: A simple to use, highly modular, and extremely configurable static content generator
---
<p class="lead"><strong>Wyam is different.</strong> It's not a Jekyll clone (not that there's anything wrong with that) and it's not designed around blogs (though it's great at those too). Wyam is a static <em>content</em> generator and can be used to generate web sites, produce documentation, create ebooks, and much more. Since everything is configured by chaining together flexible modules (that you can even write yourself), the only limits to what it can create are your imagination.</p>

<div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">Wyam is currently under heavy development, but it is usable today. Read on for more information if you want to get started now and help influence it's future direction.</div>

